name: CarRentals
0:
”Alexa, open car rentals.”
”Find a car for me in Seattle from April twenty first to April twenty fifth.”
”Book car number four.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: car rentals
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Book a rental car in minutes with the CarRentals skill. Just say "Alexa, open car rentals". And then tell Alexa where and when you want the rental car. Alexa would tell you the different car categories that are available, i.e. Economy Cars. Pick a car category and Alexa would tell you 5 available cars in the category with the lowest price. Pick the car number and Alexa would book your car for you. 

You would need to set up account linking for the first time you book through this skill. Once set up, book a rental car can take you less than 1 minute. 

* Please note that pre-pay rental car inventory is not available through this Alexa skill *
